summary: A replacement of the Iron Mace. Looks awesome.
descriptionHtml:
Forged from the fires of my mums basement comes a mod like no other...
A Black and Gold model replacement for the Iron Mace.

[url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=3565#content]Click here for Standalone Craftable Edition[/url]

Install:
Extract to your Skyrim/Data folder
(Warning: It will overwrite any other Iron Mace replacement mods)
author: Justin Davis
